;※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※
;"ENCOUNTER" events (extra syntax)
;"ENCOUNTER"系イベント（エクストラ構文）
;First Meeting
;※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※
@M_KOJO_EGG_ENCOUNTER_K50
;初対面、挨拶のタイミング
;TALENTの変更はここでどうぞ。
;経験の変更は齟齬が出る場合がありますので、CSVを修正し同梱する事を推奨します
PRINTFORMDW You come across a young blonde girl, dressed in red and white.
PRINTFORMDW Her attention seems to be focused on a cute little doll.
PRINTFORMDW You're about to offer greetings when a sneer suddenly appears on her face.
PRINTFORML 「Ew, no.」
PRINTFORMDW She extends her hand and a bright orb appears in the middle of it.
PRINTFORML ＼　Bang!　／
PRINTFORMDW The doll evaporates into nothingness.
PRINTFORMDW ...
PRINTFORMDW You're still processing what just happened when the young girl turns and faces you with a look of intrigue.
PRINTFORML 「So, what's your name?」
PRINTFORMDW Snapping back to reality, you tell her your name.
PRINTFORML 「"%CALLNAME:MASTER%"...」
PRINTFORML 「Oh! You're that outsider people have been talking about.」
PRINTFORML 「My name's Flandre Scarlet. I'm Remilia's younger sister.」
PRINTFORMDW That would mean she's a――
PRINTFORML 「Approaching a vampire? You're pretty brave.」
PRINTFORML 「Or maybe you're just stuuupid～!」
PRINTFORMDW "Probably a bit of both", you think to yourself.
PRINTFORMDL Regardless, you can immediately tell this girl is trouble.
PRINTFORMDW %BREAKENG(@"Not wanting to hang around her for longer than you have to, you tell her it was nice meeting her and begin to walk away. Quickly.")%
PRINTFORMDW ...
PRINTFORML 「Hey!」
PRINTFORMDW She calls for you. Unfortunately, it seems you're not getting away just yet. You turn around and face her again.
PRINTFORMDW An innocent, almost angelic, smile appears on her face. Maybe she's not that bad?
PRINTFORML 「Before you go――」
PRINTFORMDW She inches closer to you and a mischievous smile appears across her face. This girl is impossible to read.
PRINTFORML 「――will you play with me～?」
PRINTFORMDW Regardless of how difficult it is to get a good read on her, this request of hers immediately sets off the alarm bells in your head.
PRINTFORMDW Trying to sidestep her request, you tell her that unfortunately, you don't have the time to play with her dolls.
PRINTFORMDW ...
PRINTFORMDW The atmosphere around you becomes deafeningly quiet. Did you insult her by implying she played with dolls?
PRINTFORMDW She is a vampire, after all. Although she appears young, she's no doubt older than you by a good couple of centuries.
PRINTFORMDW You tense up ready for the worst, when――
PRINTFORML 「Hahaha! You're funny～」
PRINTFORMDW She erupts into laughter and as you begin to loosen up...
PRINTFORMDW ――!
PRINTFORMDW Suddenly someone tightly grips you from behind, you can't break free.
PRINTFORMDW You turn your head to view your assailant and are met by... another Flandre?
PRINTFORMDW Twins? No, this is some ability of hers, no doubt.
PRINTFORML 「But you know that's not what I'm talking about～」
PRINTFORMDW Another one appears on your left, then another on the right.
PRINTFORMDW The three not holding you speak in unison.
PRINTFORML 「I'm talking about the most fun thing in all of Gensokyo!」
PRINTFORMDW Then the one gripping you whispers in your ear.
PRINTFORML 「Daan～ Ma～ Kuu～」
PRINTFORMDL
PRINTFORMDL Play with her?
CALL ASK_YN()
IF !RESULT
	IF CFLAG:15:現在位置 == CFLAG:TARGET:現在位置 || CAN_MOVE(CFLAG:15:現在位置, CFLAG:MASTER:現在位置)
		PRINTFORMDW Before you can respond, another voice appears from nowhere.
		IF !CFLAG:15:面識
			PRINTFORMDW You don't recognize it.
		ELSEIF CFLAG:15:面識
			IF TALENT:15:恋人
				PRINTFORMDW You recognize it instantly. It's your lover, Sakuya.
			ELSEIF TALENT:15:思慕 || TALENT:15:セフレ == 1
				PRINTFORMDW You recognize it instantly. It's Sakuya.
			ELSE
				PRINTFORMDW You recognize it instantly. It's the mansion's head maid, Sakuya.
			ENDIF
			CALL CHARA_TEXT(15,@"「Young mistress, I apologize for any interruption.」","l")
			CALL CHARA_TEXT(15,@"「It's your sister. She would like a word with you.」","l")
			CALL CHARA_TEXT(15,@"「She said it's rather urgent.」","w")
			PRINTFORMDW Flandre looks puzzled for a moment, then surprised.
			PRINTFORML 「Remi...? Oh, that was quick! I'll go see her now!」
			PRINTFORMW 「Bye, %CALLNAME:MASTER%～」
			PRINTFORMDW And with that, she's off.
			PRINTFORMDW It seems like you've made a rather eccentric little friend.
			IF !CFLAG:15:面識
				PRINTFORMDW You turn to the maid. She bows to you and then vanishes instantaneously.
			ELSEIF TALENT:15:恋人 || TALENT:15:愛欲
				PRINTFORMDW Sakuya uses her power and 'teleports' to your side.
				CALL CHARA_TEXT(15,@"「Are you okay, dear?」","l")
				PRINTFORMDW She holds you tightly, making sure you're alright, then motions towards a teapot.
				CALL CHARA_TEXT(15,@"「I've left you some tea. Please drink it and recuperate.」","w")
				PRINTFORMDW Sakuya gives you a kiss, and then vanishes.
				CALL MUTUAL_KISS(15)
			ELSE
				PRINTFORMDW Sakuya then speaks up.
				CALL CHARA_TEXT(15,@"「Are you okay, %CALLNAME:MASTER%?」","l")
				CALL CHARA_TEXT(15,@"「I've left you some tea. Please drink it and recuperate.」","w")
				PRINTFORMDW Sakuya then bows to you and then vanishes instantaneously.
			ENDIF
			CFLAG:[[フラン]]:現在位置 = KICKOUT()
			CFLAG:15:現在位置 = KICKOUT()
		ENDIF
	ELSE
		PRINTFORMDW You decide to "play" with her.
		PRINTFORMDW As soon as you accept her request, her doppelgangers disappear.
		PRINTFORMDW The one who was facing you gets directly in your face.
		PRINTFORMDW Her eyes are sparkling and a smile beams across her face.
		PRINTFORML 「Really? Hooray!」
		PRINTFORMDW She jumps backward and creates some distance between the two of you.
		PRINTFORML 「Try to keep me entertained.」
		PRINTFORMDW She begins to rise, exerting her power. You prepare yourself.
		PRINTFORML 「And don't worry――」
		PRINTFORMDW A myriad of bullets spread out from her, all ready to fire at you.
		PRINTFORMW 「――I'm a merciful God of Destruction!」
		PRINTFORMDW Here she comes!
		PRINTFORMDW .........
		PRINTFORMDW ......
		PRINTFORMDW ...
		IF ABL:[[フラン]]:戦闘能力 > ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力
			PRINTFORMW 「Hahaha! You suck at this!」
			PRINTFORML You collapse to the ground. You're battered, bruised and completely exhausted.
			PRINTFORMDW "What the hell was I thinking agreeing to this?" you say to yourself.
			PRINTFORMDW The small vampire flies down and stands above you, looking down on you with a smile on her face.
			PRINTFORML 「You make some funny faces and noises when you're struggling for your life!」
			PRINTFORMDW You're unable to even speak due to panting for breath.
			PRINTFORMDW All you can think to yourself as you lay there, exhausted but still somehow alive, is, "Glad to hear it."
			PRINTFORMDL She extends her hand to help you up.
			PRINTFORMW 「You know, for a weakling. You're pretty fun～」
			PRINTFORMDL You try to take her hand, but at this point, you're so tired you can't even move it.
			PRINTFORMDW She takes her hand away.
			PRINTFORML 「Hehe～ We should play again soon!」
			PRINTFORMDW There's that innocent smile again...
			PRINTFORMW 「You'll come back, right?」
		ELSEIF ABL:[[フラン]]:戦闘能力 == ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力
			PRINTFORML 「Hahaha!」
			PRINTFORMW 「This is so fun!」
			PRINTFORMDW Both of you are going blow for blow.
			PRINTFORML 「To keep up with me... Like this!」
			PRINTFORML 「Hah... Hah...」
			PRINTFORMW 「Incredible!」
			PRINTFORMDW You're exhausted. You need to finish this quickly.
			PRINTFORMDW Fortunately, she also seems to be tiring herself out.
			PRINTFORMDL Since you're both tired, you make a suggestion.
			PRINTFORMDW One final ultimate attack.
			PRINTFORMDW Flandre's eyes light up.
			PRINTFORMW 「Hahaha! What a great idea!」
			PRINTFORMDW Both of you channel your energy into one last attack.
			PRINTFORMDL
			PRINTFORMDW 3...
			PRINTFORMDW 2...
			PRINTFORMDW 1...
			PRINTFORMDW Fire!
			PRINTFORMDL
			PRINTFORMDW Both of you fire an immense ball of energy at each other.
			PRINTFORMDW As they're about to collide, both of you reali――
			PRINTFORMDL ＼　KA-BOOM!　／
			PRINTFORMDW The explosion causes both of you to get flung backwards into the wall.
			PRINTFORMDW You both fall to the ground...
			PRINTFORMDW After a couple minutes you manage to stand back up, barely.
			PRINTFORMDW Flandre is standing across from you in a similar state.
			PRINTFORMDW You both grin at each other.
			PRINTFORMDW She speaks up.
			PRINTFORMW 「Hah... ready... for Round... Two?」"
		ELSEIF ABL:[[フラン]]:戦闘能力 < ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力
			PRINTFORML 「Hah... Hah... y-you're... pretty good...!」
			PRINTFORML 「But not... good... eno――」
			PRINTFORMDW %BREAKENG(@"Before she can finish speaking, you appear directly in front of her, palm open, about to fire off a magical blast point blank in her face.")%
			PRINTFORMDL She's completely stunned.
			PRINTFORMDW In no reality did she think this scenario played out like how it did.
			PRINTFORMDW She was supposed to win, not you!
			PRINTFORML 「Wh-wha...? How――」
			PRINTFORMDW Interrupting her again, you let out one, final devastating attack!
			PRINTFORMDW ...
			PRINTFORMDW ＼　Flick～　／
			PRINTFORMDW ...
			PRINTFORML 「Oww! That hurt, you jerk!」
			PRINTFORMDW She starts rubbing her forehead. You smile and apologize for being too rough.
			PRINTFORMDW Her eyes immediately begin sparkling.
			PRINTFORMDW As she looks up at you your face, you can't help but notice the little red mark you left on her forehead.
			PRINTFORML 「'Too rough'?!」
			PRINTFORMDW With a smile on her face and a renewed second wind, she grabs your hands and starts dancing around in a circle with you.
			PRINTFORML 「That was great! You're incredible!」
			PRINTFORML 「Hahaha～!」
			PRINTFORMDW Unbelievable. Was that destructive force you just fought really this innocent little vampire?
			PRINTFORML 「Hey-hey! Can we play again?」
			PRINTFORML 「This time, I'll go all out!」
			PRINTFORMDW ...This time?
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ELSE
	PRINTFORMDW You decline the opportunity to play with her, once again citing that you don't have the time.
	PRINTFORMDW Her expression immediately turns sour.
	PRINTFORML 「Tch! Booo-ring～」
	PRINTFORML 「Guess I'll go prank some of the maids...」
	PRINTFORMDW You say your goodbyes, which she completely ignores.
	PRINTFORML 「...Maybe play with Tupai?」
	PRINTFORMDW You leave with all your blood in one place and your skin intact.
	PRINTFORMDW It seems you'll live to see another day.
ENDIF
PRINTFORML
PRINTFORML
PRINTFORML
CALL KOJO_EGG_OPTION_K50_RESULT_1
RETURN 1

